            <publicationStmt>
                <p>This document contains the text of the Vilna edition of the Mishnah, slightly normalized and all punctuation removed, as the
                    basis for the alignment of the witnesses to the text of the Mishnah. The text
                    below uses the unvocalized text at <ptr target="http://he.wikisource.org/wiki"
                    />, corrected to reflect the text of Yakhin u-Boaz. Changes are introduced as
                    necessary to account for varying textual traditions to allow for proper pointing
                    from the witness files to ref.xml<!-- Bibliography -->
                </p>
            </publicationStmt>
